## gk graph

Open a visual commit graph in GitKraken Client (default) or GitLens/VS Code

```
gk graph [flags]
```

### Options

```
  -k, --gitkraken   Open in GitKraken Client
  -l, --gitlens     Open in GitLens
  -h, --help        help for graph
```
